\v 1 Kwasekusithi ngomnyaka wesikhombisa, nge\add nyanga\add* yesihlanu, ngolwetshumi lwenyanga, abathile babadala bakoIsrayeli beza uku\add za\add*buza iN\nd kosi\nd*\x + 8.1.\x*, bahlala phambi kwami\x + 14.1.\x*.
