\v 27 Ngakho, ndodana yomuntu, khuluma kuyo indlu yakoIsrayeli, uthi kubo: Itsho njalo iNkosi uJehova: Lakulokhu oyihlo bangihlambazile, ngokuthi baphambeke isiphambeko bemelene lami\x + Hlab. 78.57.\x*.
\v 28 Lapho sengibalethe elizweni, engaphakamisela isandla sami ngalo ukuthi ngibanike lona\x + 20.5.\x*, babona lonke uqaqa oluphakemeyo, lazo zonke izihlahla eziqatha, bahlaba khona imihlatshelo yabo, banikela khona isicunulo somnikelo wabo\x + Isa. 57.5. 65.7.\x*\x + 6.13.\x*, bafaka khona iphunga labo elimnandi, bathulula khona iminikelo yabo yokunathwayo\x + 6.13.\x*\x + 20.41.\x*.
