\s Ilizwi leN\nd kosi\nd* ngeningizimu
\p
\v 45 Ilizwi leN\nd kosi\nd* lafika kimi futhi lisithi:
\v 46 Ndodana yomuntu, misa ubuso bakho ngasendleleni yeningizimu\x + 6.2.\x*\x + 21.2.\x*, utshumayele ngaseningizimu\x + 21.2.\x*\x + Amos 7.16. Mika 2.6,11. Jobe 29.22. Isa. 55.10.\x*, uprofethe umelene legusu lensimu \add ye\add*ningizimu\x + 21.2.\x*;
\v 47 uthi kilo igusu leningizimu: Zwana ilizwi leN\nd kosi\nd*: Itsho njalo iNkosi uJehova: Khangela, ngizaphemba umlilo phakathi kwakho\x + Jer. 21.14.\x*, njalo uzaqeda phakathi kwakho sonke isihlahla esiluhlaza laso sonke\x + 21.3,4. 17.24. Luka 23.31. Jer. 25.29.\x* isihlahla esomileyo\x + 21.3,4. 17.24. Luka 23.31. Jer. 25.29.\x*; ilangabi elivuthayo kaliyikucitshwa, kodwa kuzatshiswa ngalo bonke ubuso kusukela eningizimu kuze kufike enyakatho\x + 21.4.\x*.
\v 48 Futhi yonke inyama izabona ukuthi mina N\nd kosi\nd* ngiwuphembile, kawuyikucitshwa\x + Isa. 30.33.\x*.
